of the Valley of the Wind, Super Metroid, The Iron Giant, Super Mario 64, and Legend

167
00:08:35,781 --> 00:08:36,282
of Zelda.

168
00:08:38,203 --> 00:08:42,645
So one thing we all loved about Brian's pitch was this idea of exploring the unknown universe.

169
00:08:42,805 --> 00:08:47,387
Our team was excited by the idea of building this living, breathing, colorful galaxy.

170
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,181
that people could discover.

171
00:08:51,603 --> 00:08:56,106
Character artist Dave Gurtin began to sketch our hero, starting with this lizard-inspired

172
00:08:56,466 --> 00:08:59,688
